      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i've had asthma for years but lately i feel super out of breath just walking around the house. like even just going to the kitchen makes me huff and puff. is this just part of getting older or should i be worried? i dont wanna go to the doctor if it's nothing",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
